commentary: Shaheen Shah Afridi to Bairstow, OUT gone, caught in the deep! Not that Fakhar was celebrating, having taken it at the second attempt and then nearly slid into the rope at deep backward square! Shaheen isn't bothered, though, and rolls out the Star Man, the crowd going quiet as they realise Bairstow is out... Didn't quite collar the pull as he'd have liked, in the air all the way and Fakhar did well to parry it diving high to his right and then grab it on the way down
